                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:flex gap-4">
                    <button class="size-12 border border-black/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">east</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="size-12 border border-black/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">west</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row bg-white border border-black/5 group">
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2 aspect-square overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCb2xDfITGCraWVvzZ-bOl403bJ2gUq7lmYyG3qnnYs6dokBc0LmJnZyp6iqmCUcmHeTwn32UyX4OFEvfiW9cCv9Gf4AcmBVAZ_6tjoL13Jvek-7RtDhQVyuqsb3u1Z8Ak67RvvHnKcV5X13jLYdSsxrqCvjbgpyFZtSLbvJyolcMqrOAd72s1hyhpFY2__XDWqCy9x7MGEER4uq4P5TKhoJKzApJn3SIPrwZQYlOjtXWSqffZkj0hRTyWIuCmj4dDEKGWr2qDwpzk" alt="Morning Glow Kit" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2 p-10 flex flex-col justify-center text-right">
                        <span class="text-accent text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">روتين صباحي</span>
                        <h4 class="text-2xl serif-heading mb-4">طقم إشراقة الصباح</h4>
                        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed mb-8 italic">ثلاث خطوات بسيطة لبدء يومك ببشرة حيوية ومحمية من العوامل الخارجية.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
                            <span class="text-lg font-bold">٣٨٠ ر.س</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-text-muted line-through">٤٥٠ ر.س</span>
                        </div>
                        <button class="primary-bg text-white py-4 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-black transition-colors">اقتناء المجموعة</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row bg-white border border-black/5 group">
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2 aspect-square overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA5nhq6Un5y5s8-1V-FiKRXxam6-If1GC1sbsm1iT4KaFuUauBoZZvcCQzRCNntjIQEmhSRK_zGr0GQ-uiojM8EL8LN-z9N1Dp2h_UWSpBvWZo5VgCfrCI3lQH0U3Wn3xS3-ln6WaYoW3H0HRVPL4jIUlLjPMu4UDUudxxVEjCS0YYDB9J_an7mfvj6L18DCnY8Vv2Syj9oz08IvUDhLH_Xn1N9uXvDJ8K0Y1GNUwzzBBxc7R5Dttf_h_zSKVOMRbxf3jG8Z_LkAcc" alt="Night Repair Kit" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:w-1/2 p-10 flex flex-col justify-center text-right">
                        <span class="text-accent text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">روتين ليلي</span>
                        <h4 class="text-2xl serif-heading mb-4">طقم الإصلاح الليلي</h4>
                        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed mb-8 italic">تغذية عميقة أثناء النوم لترميم الخلايا واستعادة مرونة البشرة.</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
                            <span class="text-lg font-bold">٤٢٠ ر.س</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-text-muted line-through">٥١٠ ر.س</span>
                        </div>
                        <button class="primary-bg text-white py-4 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-black transition-colors">اقتناء المجموعة</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. Before & After Gallery -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 lg:px-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-24 items-center">
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="relative aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex">
                            <div class="w-1/2 overflow-hidden border-l border-white/20">
                                <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDHAA3LJRUzdNN8gEKH__l4m2fdye5VwPmcFv29SF5uR3OxfLBY8apZ6cQPFRSf7yTOtZdYl8Ky6Q5fjEfTv_rLscZ0kIgAPe62gJdw1K2yDk_q_umwgPTeMCx608poszxrfKRehwayjwjWRetefy7QFAIAxf7asa7-TVFy3ho6wISACR5XoLAatyE273zxzVO2n71KH_Vd5uCR_poE-1Xq7-Fa15O-4RDq52LJNbFEvQ_N4Zq-TjLRAxIdKG-r6_1n0rPkwru_jNM" alt="Before" class="h-full w-auto object-cover max-w-none grayscale" style="width: 200%;">
                                <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-2 text-white text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">قبل</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-1/2 overflow-hidden">
                                <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBWkAU-n7VwR-vWI-Fc3T3KWERZNjsNVm4tQbyV2amPZVxQlXbCsMGwpqQlZjTmh-XsHRAlwwNJWkJYbuDlMcN3pBtn4MEiKh3aMX0IGBCgWqYt30eNaAiRwIN_OEy9RDl4GYzDIv-4E-QwOkir25AssdiLJR9euITPEZaOq0B4dUvjHa8ZllcuW_yZosjW4E-Kbi7JoNhK1BLRZToKutUJtcyKPWEE9lUeTS55fJB4IJp8twMkvhiZJlp9O3IQaIlSFg-xe7V-lDw" alt="After" class="h-full w-auto object-cover max-w-none" style="width: 200%; transform: translateX(-50%);">
                                <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 bg-primary/80 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-2 text-white text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">بعد ٢٨ يوم</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-white/50 z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="size-10 rounded-full border border-white/50 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md flex items-center justify-center text-white">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">unfold_more</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-48 h-48 bg-[#FBF8F4] -z-10"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                    <span class="text-accent text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-6 block">النتائج الملموسة</span>
                    <h3 class="text-5xl serif-heading mb-8 leading-tight">الفرق الذي <br>تستحقينه</h3>
                    <p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 serif-heading italic">في "عنايتي"، نلتزم بالشفافية. نتائجنا لا تعتمد على الوعود فقط، بل على دراسات سريرية وتجارب حقيقية لعميلاتنا اللواتي شهدن تحولاً جذرياً في صحة بشرتهن.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 justify-end">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">تحسن ملمس البشرة</span>
                            <div class="w-48 h-1 bg-black/5 relative"><div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 w-[92%] primary-bg"></div></div>
                            <span class="text-sm serif-heading">٩٢٪</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 justify-end">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">زيادة الترطيب</span>
                            <div class="w-48 h-1 bg-black/5 relative"><div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 w-[85%] primary-bg"></div></div>
                            <span class="text-sm serif-heading">٨٥٪</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 justify-end">
                            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">توحيد اللون</span>
                            <div class="w-48 h-1 bg-black/5 relative"><div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 w-[78%] primary-bg"></div></div>
                            <span class="text-sm serif-heading">٧٨٪</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5. The Science Behind Ingredients -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 lg:px-24 bg-[#F7F7F7]">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-24 text-center">
                <span class="text-accent text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-4 block">مختبراتنا</span>
                <h3 class="text-4xl serif-heading">علم المكونات</h3>
                <div class="w-16 h-px bg-black/20 mt-8"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
                <div class="bg-white p-12 text-center border border-black/5 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
                    <div class="size-16 rounded-full primary-bg/5 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined primary-text group-hover:text-white transition-colors">science</span>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-lg serif-heading mb-4">حمض الهيالورونيك</h5>
                    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed italic mb-6">المغناطيس الطبيعي للرطوبة، يحفظ الماء داخل خلايا البشرة لنضارة تدوم.</p>
                    <span class="text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent">ترطيب عميق</span>
                </div>
                <!-- Add other ingredients here if needed, or keep it concise as code.html -->
                <div class="bg-white p-12 text-center border border-black/5 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
                    <div class="size-16 rounded-full primary-bg/5 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined primary-text group-hover:text-white transition-colors">biotech</span>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-lg serif-heading mb-4">الريتينول (فيتامين أ)</h5>
                    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed italic mb-6">المعيار الذهبي لمكافحة الشيخوخة وتحفيز تجديد الخلايا وإنتاج الكولاجين.</p>
                    <span class="text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent">تجديد الخلايا</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-12 text-center border border-black/5 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
                    <div class="size-16 rounded-full primary-bg/5 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined primary-text group-hover:text-white transition-colors">eco</span>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-lg serif-heading mb-4">فيتامين سي</h5>
                    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed italic mb-6">مضاد أكسدة قوي يحمي من أضرار الشمس ويمنح البشرة إشراقة فورية.</p>
                    <span class="text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent">إشراق وحماية</span>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-12 text-center border border-black/5 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
                    <div class="size-16 rounded-full primary-bg/5 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined primary-text group-hover:text-white transition-colors">filter_vintage</span>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="text-lg serif-heading mb-4">النياسيناميد</h5>
                    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed italic mb-6">يعمل على تصغير المسام الواسعة وتقوية حاجز الحماية الطبيعي للبشرة.</p>
                    <span class="text-[9px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent">توازن المسام</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. Hero Banner -->
    <section class="relative h-[870px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-white">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 grayscale opacity-90 transition-all duration-1000">
            <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC_u2H7kB5FOV-75pUFfys7EPRj0gM4kWI8NvWmk6bhFs8w09gNRUQmawxx2Wtn8xnZMWEmIy9DTwLwSgE2joCKWAeCCTRa5d61W6I3036ZziO58MyLtSVfQA5UbK_BRuHaT8WmdYCCtoNaa8P1I2k6Gn7Os0-teMF6a-0OXiqRLhIsfWoXnzhU-x4XtYAr2LhmG2qkyrnOjZz1PqJThS0AU1LOfvoAbsZBoHdrOinnUY2k1BM4QepeW0mCWIo2eHtI14rUlKlwdlA" alt="Hero Banner" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-l from-black/40 via-transparent to-transparent flex items-center px-6 lg:px-40">
            <div class="max-w-3xl text-white">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-6 block text-white/80">المجموعة المختارة | خريف ٢٠٢٤</span>
                <h2 class="text-6xl lg:text-8xl serif-heading leading-[1.1] mb-8">جمالٌ يتحدث <br> بلغة الطبيعة</h2>
                <p class="text-xl opacity-90 mb-12 max-w-lg leading-relaxed font-light serif-heading italic">عن تلك اللمسة التي تعيد تعريف النور في ملامحك، وعن النقاء الذي تستحقه بشرتك في كل صباح ومساء.</p>
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center">
                    <button class="bg-white text-black px-12 py-5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all">اكتشفي الآن</button>
                    <button class="text-white border-b border-white/40 pb-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] hover:border-white transition-all">قصة المنتجات</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 7. Marquee -->
    <div class="bg-white py-6 overflow-hidden border-b border-black/5">
        <div class="flex whitespace-nowrap gap-24 animate-marquee items-center text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-text-muted">
            {% for i in 1..4 %}
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4"><span>منتجات أصلية ١٠٠٪</span></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-accent"><span>•</span><span>شحن مجاني للطلبات الفاخرة</span></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4"><span>عناية عالمية بين يديك</span></div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-accent"><span>•</span><span>دفع آمن ومرن</span></div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 8. Categories (Fصول العناية) -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 lg:px-24">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-24 text-center">
                <h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl serif-heading mb-6">فصول العناية</h3>
                <div class="w-20 h-px bg-accent mb-6"></div>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-sm tracking-widest max-w-md">انطلقي في رحلة البحث عن روتينك المثالي المصمم خصيصاً لاحتياجاتك الفريدة.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-16">
                <!-- We can use store.categories here if we want dynamic data -->
                {% for category in categories %}
                    <a href="{{ category.url }}" class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 group cursor-pointer grayscale-hover">
                        <div class="relative size-32 lg:size-40">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-black/5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
                            <img src="{{ category.image ?: 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDMiR9RFIfWPQRaEJuXVT-tlCz52RoHP3Bgkv2omrm9Lc29Z4fu3iGm9GO0ADnK-VhtTxCd6NAkx1WK1NQ2tVQmLIsVZRujpqX13sgOs7ojuEgADb7KZWuDsXhRKPduDl1d3wC_sReUiZeAxsHMWll3vQusRT12ImvzpPePGjGzq87hPZuMl5zxAPvCIBC6aNgPsRxkpmM4nZYJime00F_Fo4A2lW5LsaobdxLjTWYp5hR_2Dus4dE9EX12Xzuh9yF8E8Wf_v7IJ7Q' }}" alt="{{ category.name }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full p-2">
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">{{ category.name }}</span>
                    </a>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 9. New Arrivals (Product Grid) -->
    <section class="bg-white py-32 px-6 lg:px-24">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-20 border-b border-black/5 pb-10">
                <div class="text-right">
                    <h3 class="text-4xl serif-heading mb-3">حداثة التكوين</h3>
                    <p class="text-text-muted text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">اكتشفي آخر ما وصل من عالم الابتكار في العناية</p>
                </div>
                <a href="{{ link('products.index') }}" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent border-b border-accent/30 pb-1 hover:border-accent transition-all">الكل</a>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-x-12 gap-y-24">
                {% for product in products %}
                    <div class="flex flex-col group cursor-pointer" onclick="window.location.href='{{ product.url }}'">
                        <div class="relative overflow-hidden mb-8 aspect-[4/5] bg-[#F7F7F7]">
                            <img src="{{ product.image.url }}" alt="{{ product.name }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/5 transition-all"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center px-4">
                            <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent font-bold mb-2">{{ product.label ?: (product.is_new ? 'جديد' : 'إصدار حصري') }}</p>
                            <h4 class="text-lg serif-heading primary-text mb-3">{{ product.name }}</h4>
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-text-muted italic serif-heading mb-4">{{ product.slogan ?: 'ترطيبٌ يتغلغل في عمق الجمال' }}</p>
                            <span class="text-base font-bold tracking-widest primary-text">{{ product.price|money }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 10. Philosophy -->
    <section class="relative h-[921px] overflow-hidden">
        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDAeXEGIOL3TMNOCQ2UH0gMOQwpQPAWFgR1GxSr0UYP1s8-4SaQgdCRhTMm3xfbISha_tlK9g62Rtbpjy4Id0Y4-5XadeIP4xy50dJQFi8gGIAG2FV-8Y252n6ni2ID93_giN7_jPUKvsipnbTw5q20R8y6gZTNNlcas98IIiHZm_jqioaqElV06769flw9YPwbYoaWFt9pGdSMWe5VBv0VW5dooqiPAworDpIRHjaW3xsnTGNfox2i68O-fd3RqREcvsduB6rfBjM" alt="Philosophy" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-50">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-center p-12">
            <div class="max-w-4xl border border-white/20 p-20 backdrop-blur-sm">
                <h3 class="text-white text-5xl lg:text-7xl serif-heading mb-8 leading-tight">فلسفة النقاء والجمال</h3>
                <p class="text-white/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto serif-heading italic">
                    "نحن نؤمن بأن العناية بالبشرة ليست مجرد روتين يومي، بل هي طقسٌ مقدس من طقوس حب الذات، ننتقي فيه لكل سيدة ما يليق بنبل ملامحها."
                </p>
                <button class="bg-white text-black px-16 py-5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all">اكتشفي الفلسفة</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 11. Facial Care -->
    <section class="py-40 px-6 lg:px-24">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-32 items-center">
            <div class="group relative order-2 lg:order-1">
                <div class="overflow-hidden aspect-[3/4]">
                    <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDrPAiZqLiGKr3bCUieP_hKHrgJsl2BxJyAPpoHhZv1X6fUZDQQcpqJcw_fqsQqEztKXxo_JTnYA7byoeaFhILS3RIVSMxNDjEqY-cx3iNLrY4Kw6g_M3UA_dDX5COmJJv7FOwPblqOwhUAYBxVPigE91yZHT5RSb1bisc0tdFK-0ib8VkKH2rG9DQyZbFqqLgCO0xIwWi7D6C22BhiRHDfZeRt8t4SIQDbssIarSBhAhpTdfVdryMkW8-qhQrU2uGPoBnLK24T7eg" alt="Facial Care" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110">
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -bottom-12 -left-12 bg-[var(--bg-warm)] p-12 max-w-xs shadow-2xl border border-black/5 hidden md:block">
                    <h4 class="text-2xl serif-heading mb-4">جوهر الوجه</h4>
                    <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">حلول متكاملة تعيد للبشرة حيويتها المفقودة بلمسات طبية رصينة.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent flex items-center gap-2">استكشاف <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">west</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 flex flex-col items-end text-right">
                <span class="text-accent text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-6">افتتاحية الموسم</span>
                <h3 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl serif-heading mb-10 leading-tight">عناية مكثفة<br>ترتقي بروتينك</h3>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-lg serif-heading italic">لأن ملامحك هي انعكاس روحك، انتقينا لكِ أكثر التركيبات فعالية وصفاءً، لتعيشي تجربة المنتج الفاخر في كل قطرة.</p>
                <div class="w-24 h-px bg-black/20 mb-12"></div>
                <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBPgErDnIwnCaF4yMitQUJDp7vZpQiOx8nb_jwpGYblPic1ifnCX8_tUGR7JFLvclx7v-yAz9Yc6CBSDqc6OoE8o1rstVeRSzf2n2WoQlRe6FPzwd5_sHPK9FtZm54qlNeysIgWaUm6FOHFJTu7nyxhA16gaSj1ASMROR8rMQCB4vVWo346SxhrhhzEyf4r2uL82wS7D9tq6Z5J2mLSRxKvLAoUEjvWVb1dNNbBts2vfZmTbZQR25mp_K0yVoQqP3NXiiP9GKF_vY4" alt="Hair Care" class="w-full h-64 object-cover grayscale rounded-sm mb-12">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 12. Trust Badges -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 lg:px-24 border-t border-black/5 bg-white">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-20">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-accent font-light mb-8">verified</span>
                <h5 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">الأصالة المطلقة</h5>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-[180px]">نضمن لكِ منتجات أصلية من قلب دور الجمال العالمية.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-accent font-light mb-8">auto_stories</span>
                <h5 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">قصة المنتج</h5>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-[180px]">كل منتج لدينا يحمل تاريخاً من الابتكار والشغف بالجمال.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-accent font-light mb-8">lock</span>
                <h5 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">خصوصية وأمان</h5>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-[180px]">تجربة تسوق آمنة تماماً، تحفظ لكِ أرقى مستويات السرية.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-accent font-light mb-8">support_agent</span>
                <h5 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">استشارة الخبراء</h5>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-[180px]">فريقنا من خبراء التجميل جاهز لتقديم النصيحة لجمالك.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 13. Newsletter -->
    <section class="py-40 bg-[var(--bg-warm)] px-6 lg:px-24 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
            <span class="text-accent text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-8 block">مجلة عنايتي البريدية</span>
            <h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl serif-heading mb-10">كوني جزءاً من الحكاية</h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16 serif-heading italic">اشتركي ليصلكِ أرقى محتوى جمالي، وعروضنا الحصرية التي صُممت بعناية لتناسب ذوقك الرفيع.</p>
            <form onsubmit="return salla.form.onSubmit('newsletter.subscribe', event)" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row w-full gap-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <input name="email" class="flex-1 bg-transparent border-black/10 border-b focus:border-primary transition-colors py-4 px-6 text-sm placeholder:text-text-muted/40 outline-none" placeholder="عنوان بريدك الإلكتروني" type="email" required>
                <button type="submit" class="primary-bg text-white px-12 py-5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] hover:bg-black transition-all">اشتراك</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}